<br>
You *can* use it in NToV, but 8 out of 10 times it's gonna result in a 20 mob train on your guild.  I can count the uber encounters that DC is useful on with one hand, and I'm missing a couple fingers.  Luclin encounters just isn't plausible outside Ring of Fire.  UP, AR, Ssra, VT, The Deep...nothing DCable here...and if it is you can't get it to the named.  <br>
<br>
Saying that DC makes up for better nukes is based only on a few &quot;lower end&quot; uber encounters in the game, and it's definately not enough to make it viable.  The sad part is that at L64/65, DC pets wont be able to tank mobs that a L64 can get XP on.  This makes it even less viable as a source of XP.   <p>                 
