<br>
Crowd control needs to play a bigger role in fights and have the challenge factor that it had back in PoF/PoH days. Velious was an attempt to erase the enchanter class as a whole. Luclin made a mockery of enchanters and disguised what they did as 'crowd control' (i.e. Rapture and the Emp room adds).<br>
<br>
Some enchanters are only looking for better nukes most of the time, because on raids, that's the only thing they CAN do. And well they really don't do it well at all. Frankly VI going out and giving good nukes to enchanters is a sign of them giving up on the class.<br>
<br>
Enchanters don't really need new spells, we have all that we need. Let us actually be able to use the spells we have though.<br>
<br>
I don't want nukes. If I wanted to nuke, I would have made a wizard.<br>
<br>
Turonyen<br>
Level 60 Enchanter<br>
